Natasha Willard was studying for her A-levels when she fell ill with flu before Christmas . 
  She was diagnosed with encephalitis, an inflammation of the brain . 
  The 17-year-old is unable to move her arms and legs and can barely talk . 
  Doctors have told her family they do not know if she will make a full recovery . 
  She appeared fit and well days before she became ill . 
 